items.name: Corrupted Dino Costume
items.description: This costume can be used to make your dino look corrupted. Whilst wearing it your dino will be less likely to attract attention from real corrupted creatures, and will receive less damage from them. The costume will slowly degrade if the dino wearing it is in the Wastelands and does not hold Organic or Corrupted Polymer Nodules in its inventory.
